# CEM — End-to-End Trace: Recharging Controller

A single leaf run through every stage, start to finish, to see whether the pipeline actually holds together
in practice. Assumes Battery Source (`PWR.SUPPLY.BATT`) has already been through its own Decision Record,
since Recharging Controller's Requirements row lists it as a dependency.

